00:00:13.172 --> 00:00:18.257
Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:33.748 --> 00:00:37.166
What are you going to make?
Butterscotch Supreme Cake

00:00:45.797 --> 00:00:48.579
Ingredients required to make Butterscotch Supreme

00:00:48.758 --> 00:00:56.803
Butterscotch Syrup, Cream (Icing), Sponge Cake Base, 
Cashews-Groundnuts Crushed mix, Topping Gel, Vherries

00:01:07.304 --> 00:01:19.361
First, add a layer of butterscotch syrup to the cake base.
Then add a layer of icing cream. Add three layers like so and stack them up

00:01:25.700 --> 00:01:34.376
Cut the stacked up cake in the circle

00:01:37.266 --> 00:01:46.684
Keep the cut off cake pieces aside to make Supreme Pudding later on.

00:02:11.413 --> 00:02:17.622
Add butterscotch essence (2 drops) to some fesh cream and mix it

00:02:28.668 --> 00:02:36.390
Add enough to cover the entire cake.
Start to spread it across

00:02:58.106 --> 00:03:02.318
Once it's perfectly round, place the cake onto a cardboard base

00:03:18.246 --> 00:03:28.220
Add a layer of crushed chikki (groundnuts sweet)
 to the sides of the cake

00:03:40.505 --> 00:03:43.474
Press it gently to make it stick

00:03:52.256 --> 00:03:56.984
Stuff some yellow topping gel in a paper cone/icing cone

00:03:57.493 --> 00:04:07.429
Make concentric cirlces around the cake with the gel

00:04:10.467 --> 00:04:13.289
Flatten the gel

00:04:16.289 --> 00:04:20.439
Make a paper cone/icing cone with two butter papers

00:04:26.217 --> 00:04:33.622
Make a flower design with cream

00:04:36.301 --> 00:04:39.604
Spray a pink food color

00:04:52.745 --> 00:04:56.131
Decorate/Garnish as you like

00:05:02.314 --> 00:05:05.727
Garnish with some cherries

